**Lovense Integration Architecture**

**Becoming Protocol --- Haptic Reward Layer**

**Executive Summary**

This integration adds a \*\*physical reward channel\*\* to the existing
Becoming Protocol, allowing the AI system to deliver embodied pleasure
as part of the neurochemical reward architecture. The toy becomes
another ratchet: once experienced, its absence is felt.

**Part 1: Technical Foundation**

**API Overview**

The Lovense Standard API enables control via HTTPS POST requests. Key
capabilities:

\| Command Type \| Function \| Parameters \|

\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|

\| \*\*Function\*\* \| Direct control \| \`action\`: Vibrate:0-20,
Rotate:0-20, Pump:0-3 \|

\| \*\*Preset\*\* \| Named patterns \| \`name\`: pulse, wave, fireworks,
earthquake \|

\| \*\*Pattern\*\* \| Custom sequences \| \`pattern\`:
\"V:1;F:v,r,p;S:1000#\...\" \|

\| \*\*Stop\*\* \| Halt all \| Immediate cessation \|

**Request Structure**

{ \"token\": \"YOUR_DEVELOPER_TOKEN\", \"uid\": \"user_id\",
\"command\": \"Function\", \"action\": \"Vibrate:16\", \"timeSec\": 5,
\"loopRunningSec\": 3, \"loopPauseSec\": 1, \"toy\": \"toy_id\",
\"apiVer\": 1 }

**Infrastructure Requirements**

> 1\. \*\*Lovense Developer Account\*\* (free)

\- Register at lovense.com/sextoys/developer/join

\- Obtain developer token

\- Configure callback URL

> 2\. \*\*Lovense Remote App\*\* (user\'s phone)

\- Acts as Bluetooth bridge

\- Must be running during sessions

\- Connects toy → phone → your server

> 3\. \*\*Backend Endpoint\*\* (your Supabase/server)

\- Proxies commands to Lovense API

\- Stores toy connection state

\- Never exposes developer token to frontend

> 4\. \*\*Callback Handler\*\*

\- Receives toy status updates

\- Tracks connection state

\- Logs battery, online status

**Part 2: Database Schema**

**New Tables**

\-- Toy configuration and connection state CREATE TABLE lovense_devices
( id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(), user_id UUID REFERENCES
auth.users(id), toy_id VARCHAR(50), toy_name VARCHAR(50), \-- \'gush\',
\'lush\', etc. nickname VARCHAR(100), is_connected BOOLEAN DEFAULT
false, battery_level INT, last_seen_at TIMESTAMPTZ, created_at
TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW() ); \-- Command log (evidence + debugging)
CREATE TABLE lovense_commands ( id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT
gen_random_uuid(), user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id), device_id
UUID REFERENCES lovense_devices(id), command_type VARCHAR(20), \--
\'function\', \'preset\', \'pattern\', \'stop\' command_payload JSONB,
trigger_type VARCHAR(50), \-- \'task_complete\', \'notification\',
\'ai_session\', \'arousal_auction\' trigger_id UUID, \-- reference to
what triggered it executed_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(), success
BOOLEAN, error_message TEXT ); \-- Predefined reward patterns mapped to
system events CREATE TABLE haptic_patterns ( id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT
gen_random_uuid(), name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE, description TEXT,
command_type VARCHAR(20), command_payload JSONB, duration_sec INT,
intensity_min INT, \-- 0-20 intensity_max INT, \-- 0-20 use_context
VARCHAR(50)\[\] \-- \[\'task_complete\', \'good_girl\',
\'edge_session\'\] ); \-- Session tracking for arousal integration
CREATE TABLE haptic_sessions ( id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT
gen_random_uuid(), user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id), session_type
VARCHAR(30), \-- \'anchoring\', \'reward\', \'edge\', \'maintenance\'
started_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(), ended_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
total_commands INT DEFAULT 0, peak_intensity INT, ai_controlled BOOLEAN
DEFAULT false, notes TEXT );

